始、太容易結束，感情好脆弱。<br />\n<br />\n同類作品有「戀愛起義」入面阿sa果個故事，都係探討緊呢種即食嘅快速愛情文化。"},{"pid":"6aff0cec2f91af3d972048de6f0945f1f9e0ce0a","tid":827258,"uid":61154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6cf2dddc0edd4f9da288c4893c65bb7e928afbac","tid":827258,"uid":105400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"641f617a14615961279f076413f3987dc3a1a5f9","tid":827258,"uid":32757,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"咪懶高深啦傻鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"仆街睇完第一時間心入面都彈呢句出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"你睇唔明唔代表呢套作品眼高手低，只係你對藝術作品嘅解讀能力比人低，返去睇marvel啦咁你。"},{"pid":"0f809fc69540158efa07a8b5784cad9de8a0e0b4","tid":827258,"uid":131084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ef969573311bb502237a605212510c1b84fa088","tid":827258,"uid":39812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9fa52bd87bd3b9405230d4a356d4118ead29d913","tid":827258,"uid":39812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T21:00:22.000Z","msg":"中間橋段已經真實到有啲殘酷<br />\n最尾個twist 最深刻<br />\n加埋首黑夜不再來真係無敵<br />\n最可悲嘅現實係有唔少咁嘅女仔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T21:02:57.000Z","msg":"個種女仔愛嘅係對愛情嘅幻想而唔係愛一個人<br />\n當&ldquo;命運&rdquo;呢個前提被推翻之後<br />\n又再陷入第一去到第十二夜嘅循環"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"當知道鄭中基無偷食<br />\n佢先終於相信同陳奕迅既相遇係偶然<br />\n明白自己其實一早唔鍾意陳奕迅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e326b75706966f38e4a834b9e164a2d76d6a3cb2","tid":827258,"uid":39812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"就算唔講結局<br />\n中間嘅情節 由熱戀到喺馬路9跑<br />\n去到去到佢門口唔禁鐘入去果段<br />\n感覺好熟悉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d7d17ee1544082699c55218d72cbb57eca8442","tid":827258,"uid":131084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e326b757069